#### Using Cloud Foundry CLI

To unbind your app from your service, run `cf unbind-service APP-NAME
SERVICE-INSTANCE`, substituting `APP-NAME` with the name of your VMware Tanzu app and
`SERVICE-INSTANCE` with the name of your service. For example:

```
cf unbind-service myApp <%= service_instance_name %>
```

#### Using Pivotal Apps Manager

1. From the space dashboard, go to the **Services** tab.
1. Select your service.
1. Go to the **Overview** tab.
1. Click **Bind Apps**.
1. Under the **Bound Apps** section, click the **Edit Bindings** button
and disable the checkbox for the app you want to unbind from your service.
1. Click **Save**.
